data.description: Discover your dream home in The Reserve at Addison Creek in Bixby! This 3-bed, 3.5 bath, 3-car gem features soaring ceilings, abundant natural light, game room, an inviting courtyard entrance and a serene covered patio with fireplace with room to add a 14'x20' pol for an additional 466K. Community amenities include 2 pools, playground, trails gym, and a scenic fishing pond. Seize this exceptional opportunity to make the "Malibu Plan" you forever home!
